Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想再見你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.40,0:00:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 制服洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放進衣櫃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是有竅門的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竅門？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.90,0:00:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是學不會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是設計上的疏失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個抽屜只有日和能打開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:00:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和姐不知道怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正以那個青梅竹馬的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在轉學的地方給人製造了許多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥別這樣 把她說得好壞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.00,0:01:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.90,0:01:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是…屁股？
