Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 妳怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你問我我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我回神過來時 人就在那裡面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想妳怎麼突然轉學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.80,0:03:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在又突然用這種方式出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉學？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有轉學嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不記得嗎 就是上個月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道 妳連搬家的事也忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我什麼都想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難為情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 換的衣服呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我要換的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內褲浮在空中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:04:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.80,0:05:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昏過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪為什麼昏過去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 你為什麼拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？有拍出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是考試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那裡做什麼 健次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳來得正好 大家看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 是普通的合成照嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 你說要給我們看好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是你的裸照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者小雪的裸照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 你要怎樣賠償我 我色心無法平息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健次 這個怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果看不見就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和她果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 你讓開啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 妳是什麼時候變成幽靈的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是幽靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yahoo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 這是我的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷別人的可是犯罪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我並不知道哥哥有這種癖好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次需要時說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 誤會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是給日和…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人看到妳的裸體 應該會驚慌失措的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 小雪看不見妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我才看得見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我變成幽靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真搞不懂 妳為什麼會變成幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不安哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…是怎麼了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是既然都變成這樣了 煩惱也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要好好享受幽靈生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳應該認真煩惱一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:42.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 難道明天有考試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 我來教你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是跟小健在一起最開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考試結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下子可以自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.10,0:09:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我有預定事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.90,0:09:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經有我了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太不合群了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在衣櫃裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼會在這地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑哦 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在學校裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經被關在這裡過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面的小健也打不開門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果我們倆 一直哭到小健的爸爸回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候小健擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手一直拍門 拍到紅腫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時好溫馨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:52.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對小健…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 我還有腳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是剛才是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 開門啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說要跟我一起出來玩 答謝我陪你讀書 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上公園太無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為人們只看到衣服鞋子 而引起一陣騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼妳想去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想玩咖啡杯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡人太多 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就小餐廳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們用兩根管子一起喝一杯果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣很浪漫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一點也不覺冷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對哦 我是幽靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 帶妳來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會啊 這裡很浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.00,0:13:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有今天才有的限定服務哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有喝到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 我可以永遠不消失就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好黑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說沒有事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那麼快開門 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你是在等我來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛好湊巧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳這樣突然出現突然消失 我怎麼可能專門等妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候的吸管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種東西扔掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 隨便妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼妳會變成幽靈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我會在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳的腳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次也發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽靈常發生這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會…妳會消失吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那種事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次也是很快就恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢復…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 恢復吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別嚇我啦 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間比上次用得久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我真的會消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天是白色情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要一點紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳今年送我巧克力 但是後來又收回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有這回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我沒義務回報妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這次算特例
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會送妳禮物的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送我什麼什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳等明天就知道是什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我們也一起渡過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟轉學時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和回來後 我才真正明白自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果以後再也無法相見 我不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道必須睡 但又睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,護士說這是因為明天動手術前吃的藥生效了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手術不知會不會成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒什麼好後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:17:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心中…卻又不知道在掛念著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起床啦 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我遲到了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們再過一次白色情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帶妳去妳喜歡的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.30,0:19:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 大家都在看哦 會不會難為情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有妳在我比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這次再消失 以後可能就見不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就一直留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.50,0:19:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳好漂亮 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難為情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准妳到別處去 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會永遠留在這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明可以感覺到小健
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛妳 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.00,0:23:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想就這樣永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.70,0:23:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.60,0:23:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只有這個 將就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我是想把巧克力 交給小健的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不想轉學的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我並不想跟小健分開的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.80,0:24:29.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.20,0:24:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像還有點悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.20,0:24:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前的事…很對不起 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.80,0:24:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 妳在胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.60,0:24:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.60,0:24:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.40,0:24:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只會留下傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.20,0:24:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到妳？這是什麼意思 日和？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.10,0:24:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.70,0:25:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.10,0:25:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.90,0:25:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我決不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.90,0:25:09.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這個戒指的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.70,0:25:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.60,0:25:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.50,0:25:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又留下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.70,0:25:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節那天 日和送給我的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.30,0:25:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來一直藏在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.30,0:25:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.60,0:26:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說出這麼害羞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.00,0:26:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.10,0:26:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次換我回應日和的告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.00,0:26:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管日和身上發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.60,0:26:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.40,0:26:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.00,0:26:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.40,0:27:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.30,0:27:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.70,0:27:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全記不得以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.60,0:27:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.90,0:27:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只記得一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.40,0:27:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡的人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.10,0:27:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做小健
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.90,0:27:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是那個「小健」 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.30,0:27:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 又答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.70,0:27:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是妳最擅長的學科
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.60,0:27:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遊樂園裡面 我最喜歡的項目是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.10,0:27:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡杯 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.60,0:27:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難為情 根本喝不出味道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.10,0:27:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是妳想這樣喝一次不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.40,0:28:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我什麼都瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.50,0:28:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻不太能夠想起自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.50,0:28:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 那個戒指…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.50,0:28:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.50,0:28:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.80,0:28:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼在哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.20,0:28:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
